Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.spigot.core.hooks

Interface FakePlayerClassGenerator.IFakePlayer

Enclosing class:
FakePlayerClassGenerator
public static interface FakePlayerClassGenerator.IFakePlayer
The interface that is implemented by all fake players to allow easy identification.

It also contains some internal methods that are used by the generated subclass. It is not recommended to use these methods.
